urg, S.P., Melillo, J.M., Wander, M.M., Parton, W.J., Wilhelm, W.W., Sustainable biofuels redux (2008) Science, 322, pp. 49-50; Rosenthal, R.E., (2006) GAMS - A Users' Guide (Version 22.5), , GAMS Development Corporation, Washington, USA; Sahinidis, N.V., Grossmann, I.E., Fornari, R.E., Chatrathi, M., Optimization model for long range planning in the chemical industry (1989) Comput. Chem. Eng., 13, pp. 1049-1063; Searchinger, T., Heimlich, R., Houghton, R.A., Dong, F., Elobeid, A., Fabiosa, J., Tokgoz, S., Yu, T., Use of US croplands for biofuels increases greenhouse gases through emissions from land-use change (2008) Science, 319, pp. 1238-1240; Smith, T.C., Kindred, D.R., Brosnan, J.M., Weightman, R.M., Shepherd, M., Sylvester-Bradley, R., (2006) Wheat as a Feedstock for Alcohol Production, , HGCA, London, UK; Tsiakis, P., Shah, N., Pantelides, C.C., Design of multi-echelon supply chain networks under demand uncertainty (2001) Ind. Eng. Chem. Res., 40, pp. 3585-3604; Williams, H.P., (1985) Mathematical Building in Mathematical Programming, , John Wiley & Sons Ltd., Chichester, UK; Zamboni, A., Bezzo, F., Shah, N., Spatially explicit static model for the strategic design of future bioethanol production systems. 2. Multiobjective environmental optimization (2009) Energy Fuels, 23, pp. 5134-5143","Bezzo, F.; CAPE-Lab, Dipartimento di Principi e Impianti di Ingegneria Chimica, Università di Padova, Via Marzolo 9, I-35131 Padova, Italy; email: fabrizio.bezzo@unipd.it",,,,,,,,09608524,,BIRTE,21641206,"English","Bioresour. Technol.",Article,Scopus,2-s2.0-79959590256
